+- `missions/exact-ns-phase-locking-firewall/library-inbox/step-003-exploration-001-canonical-second-budget-seed-classification.md`
+
+## Constraints
+
+- Work with finite helical support ledgers as the exact objects.
+- Keep mandatory conjugate completion and recursive closure as frozen rules.
+- Do not treat packet-role language as part of the search object.
