+# Meta Note - Step 004 Exploration 002
+
+## What Worked
+
+- Splitting the closure reasoning into
+  mirror-cross spill
+  and
+  positive-positive cross-scale spill
+  made the obstruction sharper.
+  The budget already dies on the cheapest conjugate-complete ordered pairs, and
+  the cross-scale witnesses then act as backup confirmation.
+- Testing one low-dimensional coincidence guard
+  `d = b + c`
+  was enough to show that geometric folds only change which target spills
+  first, not the closure verdict.
+
+## Reusable Lesson
+
+- On recursively exact support audits, do not look only at the most thematic
+  positive-positive couplings.
+  Conjugate-complete mirror-cross pairs can kill the budget earlier and more
+  robustly.
+
+## Caution
+
+- A low-dimensional coincidence inside a live family should be checked as a
+  guard, but it should not be promoted into a new canonical family unless it
+  changes the abstract repeated-orbit pattern.
