+
+## What Worked
+
+- Treating the tidy seven-orbit star ledger as a pseudo-survivor only for the
+  enlargement pass kept the step honest while still explaining why Chain Step 3
+  is unearned.
+- Enlarging on a conceptually relevant forced orbit and then watching a simpler
+  mirror-cross difference orbit reappear made the pseudo-survivor diagnosis
