+
+## Reusable Lesson
+
+- When a seed dies by first-pass spill, the enlargement pass does not need a
+  complicated new family.
+  It only needs one admissible orbit restoration plus a fresh closure pass to
+  show that pruning was doing all the apparent stabilizing work.
+
+## Caution
+
+- A third-budget negative still remains class-limited.
+  Do not turn a clean pseudo-survivor failure into mission-level termination or
+  automatic escalation.
