+# Exploration 003 Goal - Enlargement Audit And Budget-Limited Verdict
+
+## Objective
+
+Apply at least one admissible enlargement test to every apparent third-budget
+survivor, or package a clean current-budget negative if no honest survivor
+remains after the closure audit.
+
+## Success Criteria
+
+- Every apparent survivor gets at least one explicit admissible enlargement
+  test.
+- The report states whether Chain Step 3 is genuinely earned or whether
+  controller review is still required.
+- The final verdict stays class-limited to the current budget.
+
+## Failure Criteria
+
