+- `missions/exact-ns-phase-locking-firewall/steps/step-003/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md`
+- `missions/exact-ns-phase-locking-firewall/controller/decisions/decision-004.md`
+
+## Constraints
+
+- Keep every closure-forced mode in the ledger immediately.
+- Treat lower-budget spill modes as inherited clues, not as automatic proofs
+  for every third-budget seed.
+- Do not derive projected ODEs yet.
