+### Pass 0 - conjugate completion
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The active ledger becomes
+
+  ```text
+  S_0 = { ±a, ±b, ±c, ±d, ±p, ±q, ±r }.
+  ```
+
+### Pass 1 - seed-orbit pairs
