+### Low-dimensional coincidence guard
+
+- `[INFERRED]` The coincidence
+
+  ```text
+  d = b + c
+  ```
+
+  does **not** rescue the family and does **not** create a new budget family.
+- `[VERIFIED]` In the bridge-guard representative, the ordered pair
